name: Pokemon Uranium
description: Pokémon Uranium is a free fangame made in RPGmaker XP. The game is complete, with the latest build being Version 1.2.4. The game takes place in the Tandor region, where the player must collect 8 Gym Badges in order to compete in the Tandor Regional Championship. Along the way, the player must fill up their Pokedex with more than 150 different species of Pokémon.
